  "video_id": "OtyD9EXB2pA",
  "title": "Why Chocolate Diamonds Are So Expensive | So Expensive",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 4640.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] Rihanna wore a $130,000 Chocolate Diamond"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 4640.0,
      "end_time": 7990.0,
      "text": "necklace to the 2018 Grammys."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 7990.0,
      "end_time": 10483.0,
      "text": "And these Chocolate Diamond earrings that J-Lo likes"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 10483.0,
      "end_time": 13741.0,
      "text": "to borrow: just over $16,000,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 14232.0,
      "end_time": 16116.0,
      "text": "but it wasn&#39;t that long ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 16116.0,
      "end_time": 19250.0,
      "text": "when brown diamonds would have never made the red carpet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 19251.0,
      "end_time": 22938.0,
      "text": "selling for six times less than they do today."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 23613.0,
      "end_time": 25146.0,
      "text": "So what changed?"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 25779.0,
      "end_time": 28373.0,
      "text": "Why are Chocolate Diamonds so expensive?"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 30244.0,
      "end_time": 33740.0,
      "text": "Diamonds get their color by how they&#39;re formed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 33673.0,
      "end_time": 36492.0,
      "text": "whether it was a different element that got pulled"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 36492.0,
      "end_time": 37596.0,
      "text": "into the carbon structure."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 37997.0,
      "end_time": 41552.0,
      "text": "Like boron, which gives diamonds a beautiful blue hue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 42360.0,
      "end_time": 44469.0,
      "text": "or maybe it was close to a natural source"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 44469.0,
      "end_time": 47328.0,
      "text": "of radiation, making them appear green."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 48110.0,
      "end_time": 52157.0,
      "text": "Whatever the reason, diamonds come in a rainbow of bright,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 52157.0,
      "end_time": 56303.0,
      "text": "beautiful colors, and then there are brown diamonds."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 56546.0,
      "end_time": 59106.0,
      "text": "For centuries, brown diamonds were cheap."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 59106.0,
      "end_time": 61317.0,
      "text": "They were typically low in quality"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 61317.0,
      "end_time": 63204.0,
      "text": "and had lots of imperfections."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 63762.0,
      "end_time": 67310.0,
      "text": "So jewelers didn&#39;t want them, especially when they"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 67310.0,
      "end_time": 70858.0,
      "text": "could use brighter pink, blue, or yellow diamonds."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 71266.0,
      "end_time": 74781.0,
      "text": "Instead, brown diamonds were used as tools to drill through"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 74781.0,
      "end_time": 77300.0,
      "text": "rocks and cut glass."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 77300.0,
      "end_time": 80300.0,
      "text": "But in 1986, Argyle Mine opened."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 80578.0,
      "end_time": 83826.0,
      "text": "Today, it produces more diamonds than any other mine"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 83826.0,
      "end_time": 84860.0,
      "text": "in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 84860.0,
      "end_time": 87210.0,
      "text": "Most of them being brown diamonds."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 87393.0,
      "end_time": 90378.0,
      "text": "And while it&#39;s been said that the quality of Argyle stones"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 90378.0,
      "end_time": 91791.0,
      "text": "is not equal to their quantity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 91791.0,
      "end_time": 94633.0,
      "text": "companies have still managed to find a market."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 95291.0,
      "end_time": 98512.0,
      "text": "One company in particular being Le Vian Corp."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 98655.0,
      "end_time": 102418.0,
      "text": "- We found these beautiful, natural fancy color brown"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 102418.0,
      "end_time": 105470.0,
      "text": "diamonds that were coming out of the Argyle Mine"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 105470.0,
      "end_time": 109283.0,
      "text": "of Australia that were quite underappreciated."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 109525.0,
      "end_time": 111120.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] That&#39;s Eddie LeVian."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 111120.0,
      "end_time": 112977.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s the CEO of Le Vian Corp."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 113319.0,
      "end_time": 117370.0,
      "text": "Le Vian trademarked the name Chocolate Diamonds in 2000,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 117370.0,
      "end_time": 120501.0,
      "text": "giving it a monopoly on the market for these particularly"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 120501.0,
      "end_time": 122210.0,
      "text": "named brown diamonds."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 122463.0,
      "end_time": 126425.0,
      "text": "Soon after this rebranding, Chocolate Diamonds took off."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 126425.0,
      "end_time": 128759.0,
      "text": "Google searches for \"Chocolate Diamond\" went"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 128758.99999999999,
      "end_time": 133760.0,
      "text": "from virtually zero in 2007 to 400,000 in 2014."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 134710.0,
      "end_time": 136630.0,
      "text": "And the more popular they became,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 136630.0,
      "end_time": 138350.0,
      "text": "the more value they earned."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 138350.0,
      "end_time": 142533.0,
      "text": "- The price of Chocolate Diamonds has risen"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 143208.0,
      "end_time": 144490.0,
      "text": "more than"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 144490.0,
      "end_time": 146362.0,
      "text": "three-fold in this period of time."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 146920.0,
      "end_time": 148295.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] In the &#39;80s and &#39;90s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 148395.0,
      "end_time": 150228.0,
      "text": "gem-quality brown diamonds"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 150240.0,
      "end_time": 155240.0,
      "text": "were worth about $1,500 per carat, but now many sell"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 155293.0,
      "end_time": 158622.0,
      "text": "for up to $10,000 per carat."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 159390.0,
      "end_time": 161630.0,
      "text": "And the price of larger stones has risen"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 161630.0,
      "end_time": 165403.0,
      "text": "even more, by as much 25 times."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 165786.0,
      "end_time": 168170.0,
      "text": "Le Vian isn&#39;t the only company that has tried"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 168170.0,
      "end_time": 169984.0,
      "text": "to rebrand brown diamonds."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 169985.0,
      "end_time": 173240.0,
      "text": "Jewelers like Zales have called them other names like"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 173240.0,
      "end_time": 176800.0,
      "text": "Champagne, Cognac, and Cappuccino,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 176800.0,
      "end_time": 179591.0,
      "text": "but Chocolate was the name that really took hold."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 179591.0,
      "end_time": 184168.0,
      "text": "Given its success, we asked Eddie how the name came about."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 184168.0,
      "end_time": 186210.0,
      "text": "- The name of Chocolate many people think, \"Oh, yeah"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 186210.0,
      "end_time": 188876.0,
      "text": "because these are brown, so they put chocolate,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 188876.0,
      "end_time": 193110.0,
      "text": "but the reality was there was a friend of mine, Bill Furman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 193110.0,
      "end_time": 195683.0,
      "text": "who used to come every day after work and visit me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 195683.0,
      "end_time": 198927.0,
      "text": "and he would always bring me artisan chocolates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 198927.0,
      "end_time": 202353.0,
      "text": "and he would always talk about the special powers"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 202354.0,
      "end_time": 206754.0,
      "text": "of chocolate, how it&#39;s health benefits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 206840.0,
      "end_time": 208249.0,
      "text": "how it&#39;s an aphrodisiac,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 209366.0,
      "end_time": 211640.0,
      "text": "and I started to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 212340.0,
      "end_time": 216357.0,
      "text": "how chocoholics are passionate"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 216899.0,
      "end_time": 219428.0,
      "text": "to the food chocolate."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 219978.0,
      "end_time": 223903.0,
      "text": "And so when we did the branding of Chocolate Diamonds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 224400.0,
      "end_time": 227890.0,
      "text": "we really intended to tie in"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 227890.0,
      "end_time": 231190.0,
      "text": "to the passion that people have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 231210.0,
      "end_time": 234100.0,
      "text": "the obsession that people have to the food chocolate."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 234100.0,
      "end_time": 236335.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] Le Vian says just four percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 236335.0,
      "end_time": 238776.0,
      "text": "of brown diamonds meet its criteria."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 238776.0,
      "end_time": 242110.0,
      "text": "The diamond needs to fall within a specific shape"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 242110.0,
      "end_time": 246850.0,
      "text": "between C-4 and C-6 on the industry&#39;s color scale."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 247680.0,
      "end_time": 251400.0,
      "text": "So more like a milk rather than a dark chocolate."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 251570.0,
      "end_time": 254457.0,
      "text": "Once the right stones are ready, it&#39;s time to make jewelry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 254457.0,
      "end_time": 256372.0,
      "text": "which ups the total cost."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 257470.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258380.00000000003,
      "text": "To get a closer look, we visited"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 258380.0,
      "end_time": 262150.0,
      "text": "the jewelry company Suna Bros of NYC."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 262150.0,
      "end_time": 266688.0,
      "text": "- Many years ago, diamond cutters began to experiment"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 266689.0,
      "end_time": 270283.0,
      "text": "with different ways of placing the facets on these diamonds"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 270308.0,
      "end_time": 274270.0,
      "text": "so that they didn&#39;t appear overly dark, and it allowed light"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 274270.0,
      "end_time": 276380.0,
      "text": "to penetrate and reflect back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 276380.0,
      "end_time": 278840.0,
      "text": "which gave all of these wonderful sensations."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 278840.0,
      "end_time": 280998.0,
      "text": "- [Narrator] But Chocolate Diamonds may become harder"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 280999.0,
      "end_time": 283106.0,
      "text": "to come by in the near future."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 283890.0,
      "end_time": 286127.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s been talk that Argyle Mine"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 286127.0,
      "end_time": 287690.0,
      "text": "is running out of diamonds."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 288356.0,
      "end_time": 290409.0,
      "text": "However, John doesn&#39;t think that will stand"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 290410.0,
      "end_time": 292692.0,
      "text": "in the way of their growing popularity."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 293159.0,
      "end_time": 296474.0,
      "text": "- It would seem even at a point where Argyle may no longer"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 296475.0,
      "end_time": 301670.0,
      "text": "be mining, that the groundwork has been laid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 301670.0,
      "end_time": 305560.0,
      "text": "that the interest in a range of colored diamonds now exists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 305560.0,
      "end_time": 307801.0,
      "text": "and certainly that for brown diamonds"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 307801.0,
      "end_time": 312575.0,
      "text": "I think will sustain and probably only grow more."
    }
  ]
